'''抗老霜'''（{{lang-en|'''Anti-aging cream'''}}），主要成份為[[潤膚霜|潤膚霜]]，且聲稱具備淡化皮膚歲月痕跡的美容[[保養品|保養品]]。皮膚衰老的跡象可以包括：鬆弛、[[皺紋|皺紋]]、色素增生如黑斑、紅斑或{{link-en|老人斑|Seborrheic keratosis}}等<ref>Alexiades-Armenakas MR, et al .J Am Acad Dermatol. 2008 May;58(5):719-37; quiz 738-40.</ref>。資料顯示，部分市面上的抗老霜未能達到持久及顯著的效果，即使最頂級的產品，亦須要連續使用12個禮拜或以上，才可以最多減淡皺紋10%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.consumerreports.org/health/healthy-living/beauty-personal-care/cosmetics/wrinkle-creams/wrinkle-creams-1-07/overview/0107_cream_ov_1.htm |title=Wrinkle creams - Consumer Reports Health |publisher=Consumerreports.org |date=2011-07-28 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2010-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328213826/http://www.consumerreports.org/health/healthy-living/beauty-personal-care/cosmetics/wrinkle-creams/wrinkle-creams-1-07/overview/0107_cream_ov_1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一研究發現，部分抗老霜的抗老效果與潤膚霜基本無異<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.which.co.uk/reviews-ns/anti-wrinkle-eye-creams/index.jsp |title=Anti-wrinkle eye creams - Archive - Which? Home & garden |publisher=Which.co.uk |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2009-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090906185626/http://www.which.co.uk/reviews-ns/anti-wrinkle-eye-creams/index.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Smithers |first=Rebecca |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/money/blog/2009/aug/20/face-cream-study |title=One in the eye for anti-wrinkle creams | Money | guardian.co.uk |publisher=Guardian |date=2009-08-20 |accessdate=2012-02-14 |archive-date=2013-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718222606/http://www.guardian.co.uk/money/blog/2009/aug/20/face-cream-study |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨着民眾護膚意識日益普及，抗老霜漸漸被推廣到男性市場，現已不再僅僅是一種女性主導產品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4433343.stm |title=Drawing a line under men's wrinkles |publisher=BBC News Magazine |date=2005-04-19 |accessdate=2012-07-18 |archive-date=2009-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207175308/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/magazine/4433343.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

